body:
### Welcome to CIS APP
iOS App for RVC CIS Division.

Test APP:

1) If interested in testing please install below app and email UDID to:
c.konkol@rockvalleycollege.edu
https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/udid-tool/id377602501?mt=8

Wait for email from c.konkol@rockvalleycollege.edu before going to step 2.

2) Install App
Download and Test to iPhone/iPad:
https://ota.io/orffgd

3) Post Feedback/Issues 
https://github.com/ioscourse/CIS-APP/issues
